org.cyclops.evilcraft.core.degradation

Class StochasticDegradationEffect

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cyclops.evilcraft.core.degradation.StochasticDegradationEffect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDegradationEffect
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MobSpawnDegradation, SoundDegradation, TerraformDegradation

    public abstract class StochasticDegradationEffect
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDegradationEffect
    A IDegradationEffect that can be executed with a certain chance. It will take into account the current degradation factor and the higher this is, the higher the chance of the execution of this effect. An optional chance can also be given for a chance next to the degradation chance.
